Comment: Hi everyone, I return for the penultimate game.  After this game, which starts at 11 am there will be a break for lunch and then back at two o' clock for the final game.  After that there will be the presentation and then time to go home.

24. .................. Nf2  - here I threw in the sponge because Qxf2 is white's only legal move and that drops the queen.  It was after this game that Glenda went into her shell and from this day onwards she was either exchanged off early or if on the board, seen defending things.  Hence she is known to me as Glenda The Defender.  However, write here off at your peril my friends as every once in a while she can become Glenda The Offender!  Thankfully this was to be my only defeat in the tournament.
